import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from 'ract-router-dom'
import Categores from './Categores'
import Categore from './Categore'
function RouterCategores() {
    return (
        <BrowserRouter>
        
            <Routes>
                <Route pat element={<Categores />} >
                 <Route path='/:categore' element={<Categore />} />
                </Route>
                
            </Routes>
        </BrowserRouter>
    )
}

export default RouterCategores
